00:24:14,801 --> 00:24:16,261
Malapit na ang bisperas ng bagong taon.

485
00:24:17,406 --> 00:24:19,700
Hindi ko nga alam kung bakit kami nandito.

486
00:24:24,797 --> 00:24:28,885
Jay-jay, tigilan mo na ang paghila dito. Mukha kang magaling!
Hindi na kailangang maging conscious.

487
00:24:29,218 --> 00:24:31,818
Hindi lang ako komportable na suotin ito.

488
00:24:32,138 --> 00:24:33,639
Kinakailangan bang magsuot ng damit?

489
00:24:34,015 --> 00:24:35,391
Kumapit ka lang, Jay-jay.

490
00:24:40,021 --> 00:24:41,181
Angelo, anong nangyari sayo?

491
00:24:42,356 --> 00:24:43,399
May mali ba?

492
00:24:44,108 --> 00:24:46,694
Bakit dito tayo nagdiriwang ng Bagong Taon?

493
00:24:47,278 --> 00:24:49,238
Bakit mo pinayagan si Aries
hindi para magcelebrate kasama tayo?

494
00:24:49,947 --> 00:24:50,948
Nauna sa amin si Aries.

495
00:24:51,199 --> 00:24:52,199
Pupunta siya dito.

496
00:24:53,159 --> 00:24:54,159
Okay.

497
00:24:55,703 --> 00:24:56,703
Hanamitchi Hotel...

498
00:24:58,998 --> 00:25:01,584
Bagay talaga si Yuri ha?
Napakarami nilang branches ng hotel.

499
00:25:02,084 --> 00:25:03,724
Angelo, baka magpalit muna ako ng damit.

500
00:25:03,753 --> 00:25:05,730
Kilala ko ang may-ari ng hotel na ito. Si Yuri naman.

501
00:25:05,755 --> 00:25:07,155
Kahit wala siya ngayon sa bansa.

502
00:25:08,132 --> 00:25:09,634
Jay, ang kaibigan mong si Yuri...

503
00:25:10,051 --> 00:25:12,178
May sinabi ba siya
sa iyo bago siya maglakbay?

504
00:25:15,014 --> 00:25:16,557
Wala talaga. Bakit?

505
00:25:18,184 --> 00:25:19,184
gusto mo ba siya?

506
00:25:19,352 --> 00:25:20,019
Huh?!

507
00:25:20,353 --> 00:25:21,020
Ay...

508
00:25:21,312 --> 00:25:22,312
Jay-jay,

509
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:24,106
kahit anong mangyari...

510
00:25:26,567 --> 00:25:27,610
Basta...

511
00:25:29,111 --> 00:25:30,570
Huwag kang magalit, okay?

512
00:25:30,571 --> 00:25:32,365
Ipapaliwanag namin ang lahat mamaya.

513
00:25:33,407 --> 00:25:35,325
Hindi ko maintindihan, Lola.

514
00:25:35,326 --> 00:25:37,453
Mamaya. Ipapaliwanag namin ito.

515
00:25:38,704 --> 00:25:40,665
anong nangyayari? Bakit mamaya?

516
00:25:40,831 --> 00:25:42,749
Siguro mas mabuti na
sabihin mo sa akin ngayon, dahil...

517
00:25:42,750 --> 00:25:44,230
- Nagiging balisa na ako.
- Hindi...

518
00:25:44,502 --> 00:25:46,712
Ginoong Fernandez? Sa ganitong paraan, pakiusap.

519
00:25:47,838 --> 00:25:49,257
Halika na.

520
00:25:52,677 --> 00:25:54,303
- Ano iyon?
- Oh, wala.

521
00:25:54,971 --> 00:25:57,723
- Natapakan mo ba ang iyong damit?
- Oo, Lola.

522
00:26:07,288 --> 00:26:08,581
Kumusta, Ginoong Fernandez.

523
00:26:10,611 --> 00:26:11,988
Magandang gabi po, Ginang Fernandez.

524
00:26:13,051 --> 00:26:14,301
Madam, sa ganitong paraan.

525
00:26:14,581 --> 00:26:15,581
salamat po.

526
00:26:16,617 --> 00:26:17,910
Hi!

527
00:26:19,036 --> 00:26:20,036
Hello!

528
00:26:20,788 --> 00:26:21,788
Sir.

529
00:26:22,081 --> 00:26:23,582
- Manigong Bagong Taon!
- Magandang makita ka.

530
00:26:24,875 --> 00:26:25,918
Buti na lang nakita kita.

531
00:26:30,089 --> 00:26:31,089
Manigong Bagong Taon!

532
00:26:32,425 --> 00:26:33,425
Hello.

533
00:26:35,469 --> 00:26:36,846
- Hello.
- Magandang makita ka.

534
00:26:37,346 --> 00:26:38,346
Hello.

535
00:26:40,141 --> 00:26:41,100
Jay.

536
00:26:41,101 --> 00:26:43,977
Gusto kong makilala mo si Mr. Yumori Hanamitchi.

537
00:26:43,978 --> 00:26:45,770
At si Gng. Yakito Hanamitchi.

538
00:26:45,771 --> 00:26:46,897
Hello.

539
00:26:47,606 --> 00:26:49,525
- [sa Japanese] Hello.
- [sa Japanese] Hello.

540
00:26:49,817 --> 00:26:51,027
Tama ang ama.

541
00:26:51,736 --> 00:26:52,945
Napakaganda mo.

542
00:26:53,529 --> 00:26:54,572
[nagsasalita ng Hapon]

543
00:26:55,156 --> 00:26:55,990
salamat po.

544
00:26:55,991 --> 00:26:58,074
Hello, Jay. Ikinagagalak na makilala ka sa wakas.

545
00:26:58,075 --> 00:26:58,951
Hello!

546
00:26:58,951 --> 00:26:59,951
Gusto ko ang buhok mo.

547
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:02,038
salamat po.

548
00:27:02,039 --> 00:27:04,248
- Kamustahin mo sila.
- Hello.

549
00:27:04,999 --> 00:27:07,376
Anyway, maging komportable ka.

550
00:27:07,460 --> 00:27:08,669
Masiyahan sa party.

551
00:27:08,878 --> 00:27:10,713
- Manigong Bagong Taon.
- Manigong Bagong Taon.

552
00:27:11,714 --> 00:27:12,798
Enjoy.

553
00:27:13,341 --> 00:27:14,425
Mag-usap ulit tayo mamaya.

554
00:27:14,717 --> 00:27:15,176
Oo naman.

555
00:27:15,509 --> 00:27:16,761
Mag-usap tayo mamaya.

556
00:27:17,345 --> 00:27:18,345
Enjoy.

557
00:27:18,804 --> 00:27:19,804
Narito ang iyong bag.

558
00:27:26,912 --> 00:27:28,914
Buti na lang nandito rin si Keifer.

559
00:27:28,957 --> 00:27:30,124
Maniniwala ka ba?

560
00:27:30,149 --> 00:27:33,029
Kahit nakatalikod siya sa akin,
Hindi ko siya mapagkakamalan na iba.

561
00:27:45,054 --> 00:27:47,390
So nag-uusap na naman sila ha?

562
00:27:48,542 --> 00:27:49,877
Nasaan si Aries?

563
00:27:50,211 --> 00:27:51,253
Ano ang nangyayari?

564
00:28:02,765 --> 00:28:04,765
- Waiter... pwede bang makahingi ng tubig?
- Okay.

565
00:28:05,992 --> 00:28:06,620
Dito po Ma'am.

566
00:28:06,644 --> 00:28:10,314
Tangkilikin natin ang isang magandang pagganap
mula sa aming guest singer

567
00:28:10,606 --> 00:28:12,900
nag-render ng parehong magandang kanta.

568
00:28:13,484 --> 00:28:15,778
[applause]

569
00:28:31,544 --> 00:28:35,339
Ang kantang ito... Ito ay palaging
naging malapit sa puso ko.

570
00:28:35,506 --> 00:28:37,800
Pero mas naging espesyal dahil...

571
00:28:46,767 --> 00:28:50,855
Dapat ay tayo na.
Kaming dalawa ni Keifer...

572
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:04,492
Sige. maraming salamat po
para sa magandang rendition.

573
00:29:04,493 --> 00:29:07,037
Mangyaring, isang buong palakpakan, lahat.

574
00:29:08,414 --> 00:29:11,959
Ito ay makapigil-hininga
and spellbinding talaga.

575
00:29:12,042 --> 00:29:14,169
Syempre bata pa ang gabi.

576
00:29:14,170 --> 00:29:16,296
At hindi doon nagtatapos ang kasiyahan.

577
00:29:16,297 --> 00:29:20,508
Kaya sa yugtong ito ng programa,
Gusto kong imbitahan ang lahat...

578
00:29:20,509 --> 00:29:23,511
upang kumuha ng gitnang yugto
at sumayaw sa gabi.

579
00:29:23,512 --> 00:29:24,763
Sa lahat ng paraan!

580
00:29:25,431 --> 00:29:26,431
Sige.

581
00:29:26,765 --> 00:29:27,765
Tara na.

582
00:29:39,570 --> 00:29:40,488
Jay.

583
00:29:40,571 --> 00:29:41,739
sayaw tayo.

584
00:29:44,450 --> 00:29:45,450
Oh?

585
00:29:45,451 --> 00:29:46,868
Hindi ko alam na nakabalik ka na pala.

586
00:29:46,869 --> 00:29:47,661
Oo.

587
00:29:47,870 --> 00:29:48,870
Nasaan ang souvenir ko?

588
00:29:48,913 --> 00:29:50,079
Manigong Bagong Taon.

589
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:51,748
- Bibigyan kita mamaya, okay?
- Akin din.

590
00:29:51,749 --> 00:29:53,375
- Sayaw muna tayo.
- Aking souvenir!

591
00:29:53,501 --> 00:29:55,544
ganito. Isa, dalawa, tatlo. Pumunta ka.

592
00:30:04,011 --> 00:30:05,712
Apat, tatlo, dalawa, isa.

593
00:30:05,888 --> 00:30:06,888
Tama ba ang ginagawa ko?

594
00:30:06,972 --> 00:30:07,972
Sige na.

595
00:30:08,307 --> 00:30:09,307
sayaw lang.

596
00:30:09,934 --> 00:30:10,934
doon.

597
00:30:14,271 --> 00:30:15,271
Ang hirap!

598
00:30:15,731 --> 00:30:16,731
Hindi mo alam kung paano.

599
00:30:29,328 --> 00:30:30,663
Lumipat lang. Kaya mo yan.

600
00:30:30,871 --> 00:30:31,871
ganito.

601
00:30:33,749 --> 00:30:34,749
Dito, dito, dito.

602
00:30:35,167 --> 00:30:36,167
Ayan tuloy.

603
00:30:36,710 --> 00:30:37,710
Ganun.

604
00:30:40,965 --> 00:30:41,966
Kita mo? Nakuha mo na.

605
00:30:44,468 --> 00:30:45,468
Ilipat mo, Jay!

606
00:30:46,428 --> 00:30:47,428
doon.

607
00:30:47,888 --> 00:30:48,973
Ayan tuloy.

608
00:30:51,183 --> 00:30:52,393
Ngayon ay magagawa mo na!

609
00:31:28,095 --> 00:31:29,138
Umupo na tayo.

610
00:31:29,471 --> 00:31:30,723
Maghintay ka. Manatili tayo dito.

611
00:31:33,767 --> 00:31:36,895
Magandang gabi, sa lahat!
At isang Maligayang, Manigong Bagong Taon!

612
00:31:37,062 --> 00:31:39,897
Sa labas ng Kapistahan ng Bagong Taon...

613
00:31:39,898 --> 00:31:42,108
iba rin ang ipinagdiriwang namin.

614
00:31:42,109 --> 00:31:46,195
Ang kaarawan ng ating sariling,
Ginoong Yuri Hanamitchi!

615
00:31:46,196 --> 00:31:48,281
- Ngayon ang iyong kaarawan?
- Umakyat sa entablado!

616
00:31:48,282 --> 00:31:50,784
- Maligayang kaarawan!
- Yuri, halika dito!

617
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:56,081
Sumama ka sa akin.

618
00:31:56,457 --> 00:31:58,334
- Maligayang kaarawan!
- Halika.

619
00:31:59,335 --> 00:32:00,335
Sigurado ka ba?

620
00:32:00,336 --> 00:32:01,586
- Sige.
- Magtiwala ka lang sa akin, okay?

621
00:32:01,587 --> 00:32:03,296
Halika dito Yuri.

622
00:32:03,297 --> 00:32:04,672
Tingnan natin kung ano ang nakuha mo. Halika dito.

623
00:32:04,673 --> 00:32:06,717
Para mas tingnan natin siya di ba?

624
00:32:06,842 --> 00:32:08,093
Kumusta, Yuri.

625
00:32:09,136 --> 00:32:13,974
Happy birthday sayo. At sa aking bilang,
kantahin natin siya ng happy birthday diba?

626
00:32:14,099 --> 00:32:15,768
Isa, dalawa, tatlo!

627
00:32:15,934 --> 00:32:21,689
[kumanta ng Happy Birthday Song]

628
00:32:21,690 --> 00:32:22,690
Iyan ang espiritu.

629
00:32:22,691 --> 00:32:24,192
[kumanta ng Happy Birthday Song]

630
00:32:24,193 --> 00:32:24,902
Mas malakas!

631
00:32:24,903 --> 00:32:32,903
[kumanta ng Happy Birthday Song]

632
00:32:33,786 --> 00:32:36,413
Sige, happy birthday ulit, Yuri!

633
00:32:38,749 --> 00:32:42,961
Napakaraming ngiti para kay Yuri. Narinig namin
napakaraming dapat ipagdiwang.

634
00:32:43,087 --> 00:32:47,257
Sa katunayan, hayaan mo rin akong pormal na\
announce sa lahat ng nandito.

635
00:32:47,424 --> 00:32:52,303
Ang partnership sa pagitan ng
ang korporasyong Fernandez at Hanamitchi.

636
00:32:52,304 --> 00:32:55,599
Malaking palakpakan!
At mag-toast tayo diyan!

637
00:33:00,145 --> 00:33:02,106
Iyan ay nararapat na papuri.

638
00:33:02,314 --> 00:33:04,149
Dahilan para sa pagdiriwang.

639
00:33:07,027 --> 00:33:08,612
Binabati kita.

640
00:33:08,821 --> 00:33:11,072
At panghuli, ngunit hindi dapat madaig.

641
00:33:11,073 --> 00:33:15,618
Bilang simbolo ng tatak na ito
bagong partnership na mabubuo...

642
00:33:15,619 --> 00:33:19,247
Hayaan mo akong maging isa,
siyempre, sabihin sa lahat...

643
00:33:19,248 --> 00:33:21,332
Tungkol sa engagement nitong dalawa.

644
00:33:21,333 --> 00:33:28,340
G. Yuri Hanamitchi at walang iba kundi,
Jasper Jean Fernandez Mariano!

645
00:33:28,841 --> 00:33:31,176
Ang ganda ng mag-asawa, itong dalawang ito, tama ba?

646
00:33:40,185 --> 00:33:41,812
Mag-toast tayo!

647
00:33:43,147 --> 00:33:46,734
Mag-toast tayo sa
ang bagong kasal na mag-asawa.

648
00:33:49,987 --> 00:33:51,320
Malaki, malaking kamay.

649
00:33:51,321 --> 00:33:53,741
- Ano ang ibig nilang sabihin, Yuri?
- Mag-toast tayo!

650
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:58,500
- [sa Japanese] Cheers!
- [sa Japanese] Cheers!

651
00:34:01,415 --> 00:34:05,377
- At isang malaki, malaking kamay!
- Cheers!

652
00:34:11,133 --> 00:34:15,052
Sige. And now with that said, its's
oras na para sumayaw pa sa gabi

653
00:34:15,053 --> 00:34:18,515
kasama ang isa pa
pagtatanghal mula kay Miss Mitch.

654
00:34:25,647 --> 00:34:26,857
Binabati kita.

655
00:34:30,152 --> 00:34:31,152
Halika na.

656
00:34:31,862 --> 00:34:32,862
Sayaw tayo, Jay.

657
00:35:41,348 --> 00:35:44,351
Alam nila... alam nilang lahat.

658
00:36:03,328 --> 00:36:04,580
Alam din ba niya?

659
00:36:19,344 --> 00:36:20,721
Panaginip ba ito?

660
00:36:21,221 --> 00:36:22,222
Kasal?

661
00:36:23,515 --> 00:36:26,355
At parang alam nilang lahat.
Kaya naman kakaiba ang kinikilos nila.

662
00:36:27,561 --> 00:36:29,897
Angelo, Auntie Gemma, even Lola.

663
00:36:30,272 --> 00:36:33,275
Yuri... alam niya ang tungkol dito
nung binigay niya sakin yung singsing.

664
00:36:34,985 --> 00:36:37,112
Alam na niya noong ibinigay niya sa akin ang singsing na iyon.

665
00:36:37,988 --> 00:36:39,489
Ako na lang ang natitira sa dilim.

666
00:36:40,866 --> 00:36:43,226
Ako, yung nakipag-engage.
Ginawa akong tanga.

667
00:36:52,377 --> 00:36:53,377
Jay...

668
00:36:56,173 --> 00:36:58,592
Pabayaan mo na lang ako, Angelo, please.

669
00:37:00,302 --> 00:37:02,429
Matagal ko nang gustong ipaliwanag sayo.

670
00:37:03,055 --> 00:37:05,015
Pero hindi ko lang makuha ang tamang pagkakataon.

671
00:37:07,517 --> 00:37:08,517
pasensya na po.

672
00:37:09,686 --> 00:37:11,188
Kinailangan kong gawin ito sa iyo.

673
00:37:12,064 --> 00:37:13,357
Pero wala kaming choice.

674
00:37:16,318 --> 00:37:18,987
May choice kang sabihin sa akin.

675
00:37:19,947 --> 00:37:23,575
Bakit hindi mo sinabi sa akin?
Kailangan kong malaman ang tungkol dito!

676
00:37:24,242 --> 00:37:26,036
Hindi talaga namin alam kung paano ito sasabihin.

677
00:37:26,578 --> 00:37:28,956
At nagtitiwala kami na mayroon ka
magandang relasyon kay Yuri.

678
00:37:29,331 --> 00:37:30,791
Binigyan ka niya ng singsing.

679
00:37:31,416 --> 00:37:32,167
Kaya nag-assume kami.

680
00:37:32,167 --> 00:37:33,167
Assumed?!

681
00:37:34,711 --> 00:37:36,212
Jay, nalugi ang kumpanya...

682
00:37:36,213 --> 00:37:38,006
Pero bakit ako?!

683
00:37:40,092 --> 00:37:42,343
Oo, utang ko sa pamilya mo.

684
00:37:42,344 --> 00:37:45,180
Pero hindi ibig sabihin nun
kaya mong kontrolin ang lahat tungkol sa akin.

685
00:37:45,472 --> 00:37:47,933
Na ikaw ang magdedesisyon para sa akin.

686
00:37:48,642 --> 00:37:52,145
Angelo, hindi mo ginawa
hilingin ang aking sasabihin dito.

687
00:37:53,855 --> 00:37:55,565
Nakausap namin si Auntie Jeana tungkol dito.

688
00:37:56,110 --> 00:37:58,527
At bakit siya ang kinausap mo imbes na ako?

689
00:37:59,152 --> 00:38:00,237
Dahil nanay mo siya.

690
00:38:00,487 --> 00:38:01,697
Magulang mo pa rin siya.

691
00:38:01,722 --> 00:38:04,116
Kinausap mo ang aking ina,
pero paano si Dad?!

692
00:38:05,445 --> 00:38:07,619
Humingi ka ba ng pahintulot niya?

693
00:38:17,462 --> 00:38:18,672
Angelo...

694
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:24,094
Alam kong marami akong nagawang mali.

695
00:38:24,678 --> 00:38:26,722
Marami akong ginulo.

696
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:32,853
Pero I'm trying my best para ayusin ang lahat.

697
00:38:35,731 --> 00:38:39,860
Angelo, kasal ang pinag-uusapan dito.
Ito ang aking buhay na nakataya!

698
00:38:41,069 --> 00:38:43,321
Wala na tayong ibang makakapitan, Jay.

699
00:38:44,614 --> 00:38:45,614
Ikaw lang ang pag-asa namin.

700
00:38:47,325 --> 00:38:49,995
Nang si Mr. Hanamitchi
hiningi ang kamay mo para kay Yuri...

701
00:38:50,370 --> 00:38:51,955
Una kong sinabi na hindi.

702
00:38:52,706 --> 00:38:55,208
Pero sabi niya wala na siyang gusto.

703
00:38:57,794 --> 00:39:00,797
At bukod sa, mayroon kang isang
magandang relasyon kay Yuri.

704
00:39:01,131 --> 00:39:02,131
tama?

705
00:39:02,966 --> 00:39:04,801
Pero si Angelo, hindi kami magkasama.

706
00:39:05,260 --> 00:39:07,179
Magkakaroon ka ng komportableng buhay.

707
00:39:07,888 --> 00:39:09,431
Ito ay hindi lamang tungkol sa kumpanya.

708
00:39:10,057 --> 00:39:11,224
Tungkol din ito sa iyo.

709
00:39:12,517 --> 00:39:14,895
Isang magandang buhay ang naghihintay
kasama mo ang mga Hanamitchi.

710
00:39:15,687 --> 00:39:17,647
Madevelop ka lang
iyong relasyon ni Yuri.

711
00:39:18,106 --> 00:39:19,232
Alam kong kaya mo.

712
00:39:20,358 --> 00:39:21,443
Angelo...

713
00:39:22,861 --> 00:39:24,738
Ayokong magpakasal.

714
00:39:25,989 --> 00:39:30,077
bata pa ako. Gusto kong mag-aral.
Gusto kong magtrabaho.

715
00:39:32,329 --> 00:39:36,208
Gusto kong makuha ang mga bagay
Gusto ko sa pamamagitan ng sarili kong pagsusumikap.

